    <title>SSRF</title>
    <link href="https://www.penlab.me/2018/08/17/Web_SSRF/"/>
    <id>https://www.penlab.me/2018/08/17/Web_SSRF/</id>
    <published>2018-08-16T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-03-06T12:04:49.739Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我一直想把web安全的知识用最简单的方式阐述，今天尝试一下SSRF。<br><img src="https://ws4.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNbRwly1fukmzz68inj301y02smx0.jpg" alt=""></p><p><a href="https://ctf-wiki.github.io/ctf-wiki/web/ssrf/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SSRF</a>(Server-side request forgery)即服务器端请求伪造。</p><p><img src="/media/Web_SSRF/1.png" alt="1"></p><p>这张图中，可以看到防火墙只允许外部用户访问系统中的web服务，而系统中右边那一堆其他服务显然是外部用户无法触及到的。此时的小黑人想要攻击这些从外网无法访问的内部系统。</p><blockquote><p>攻击方式: 攻击者通过修改请求发起攻击，使服务器向第三方发起请求并返回。</p></blockquote><p> <img src="https://ws3.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNbRwly1fukpylqwn1j302s02s744.jpg" alt=""></p><p>具体看个例子:<br><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// GET方法为url传参</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">isset</span>($_GET[<span class="string">'url'</span>]))</span><br><span class="line"> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    $url = $_GET[<span class="string">'url'</span>]</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">//打开文件</span></span><br><span class="line"> $image = fopen($url,<span class="string">'rb'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">//发送合适的相应头</span></span><br><span class="line"> header(<span class="string">'Content-Type: image/png'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">//发送图片内容</span></span><br><span class="line"> fpassthru($image);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>正常的服务流程是：提供一个正常的图片网址，服务器抓到然后返回给你。<br>注意此时的图片是服务器去请求的，也就是说在防火墙内部发起的。</p><blockquote><p>那就可以绕过防火墙从内网发起请求访问内网资源。</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://ws2.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNbRwly1fukqhnpmxhj302s02sa9u.jpg" alt=""></p><p>问题发生在Url的解析上，要想办法访问localhost。如构造：<br><code>GET /?url=http://localhost/server-status HTTP/1.1Host: example.com</code><br>这样子就可以访问web服务器可以接触到而外部无法接触的资源了。<br>那么利用的关键就是Url一方面能够绕过验证检查，一方面又能够解析成本地访问(想对内网攻击)。。。<br><img src="https://ws3.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNbRwly1fukpzd2uttj302s02sa9x.jpg" alt=""><br>推荐BlackHat2017上关于SSRF的分享。</p><p>尝试结束，哈。</p>]]></content>
    
